thread.title: Steve

author: Steve
title: Steve
text: This is the first time I have used Ink Station and initial impressions are very good. Easy to follow web site, prompt delivery in the promised time frame and the product itself (laser cartridge) is of excellant quality, in fact its just as good as the named brand selling about 4 times the price. If this service and quality continues they will be my first choice. Well done guys! Steve
